## Wela'lioq (Thank You)

Wela'lioq to all the Mi'kmaq Elders, knowledge keepers, educators, and community members who have worked tirelessly to preserve and revitalize Mi'kmawisimk. This work stands on the foundation of your dedication and wisdom.

## Contact

For questions about cultural protocols, community partnerships, or appropriate use of this software, please reach out through established Mi'kmaq cultural and educational organizations.

